&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Leafony/HW-Design-Files/blob/master/AI02_SP%26PIR/AI02_SP%26PIR_PCBLayout.zip&#34;&gt;レイアウト図 SP＆PIR (Zuken)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
